sentences.english: The baseline inspection effort covers the array of routine inspections conducted by the NRC at every nuclear plant.
sentences.chinese: 基線檢查應覆蓋NRC在每座電站主導的常規監督。

sentences.english: Re-label the elapsed time column to specify Baseline time.
sentences.chinese: 重新設定消失時間列，以指定基線時間。

sentences.english: The baseline can be created from his repository workspace.
sentences.chinese: 基線可以從他的儲存庫工作區中創建。

sentences.english: An interface to take deltas against the baseline.
sentences.chinese: 用於計算出相對於基線的差值的接口。

sentences.english: The errors were amplified during the propagation from the satellite spatial states to the inter-satellite baseline.
sentences.chinese: 且由衛星空間狀態得到星間基線的過程中誤差放大。

sentences.english: Mainline is the codeline that has no baseline.
sentences.chinese: 主線是沒有基線的代碼線。

sentences.english: Products that have passed their quality checks and are approved are baselined products.
sentences.chinese: 經過質量檢查並已被批准的產品將成爲基線產品。

sentences.english: In Chapter 1, the basic concepts of VLBI were briefly described.
sentences.chinese: 第一章，介紹了甚長基線的基本概念。

sentences.english: The changing rates of baselines reflected crustal motion of different sites.
sentences.chinese: 基線長度變化率反映了測站間的地殼運動情況。

sentences.english: Once the baseline activities are done, the build process commences.
sentences.chinese: 一旦基線活動完成，構建過程就開始了。

sentences.english: The leading value represents the spacing between lines of text and is measured (in points) from baseline to baseline.
sentences.chinese: 字行間值定義了文本行基線間的舉例值。

sentences.english: Determines the baseline y-coordinate of the first line of text of the component.
sentences.chinese: 該屬性決定該控件第一行文字的基線縱座標。

sentences.english: Its “extended-baseline scenario” assumes that current law remains unchanged.
sentences.chinese: 其“延續基線的情形”假定現行法律將保持不變。

sentences.english: Make changes made to the writeable version of the current baselined architecture.
sentences.chinese: 您需要對當前基線化的結構的可寫版本作出變更。

sentences.english: SG1: Baselines of identified work products are established.
sentences.chinese: 建立已識別的工作產品的基線。

sentences.english: Baselines and package names should be synchronized to support traceability.
sentences.chinese: 基線和包的名字需要同步以支持可跟蹤性。
